Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127994,127994}Best Supporting Actress…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132165,132165}…goes to Helen Keller\Nin "The Miracle Worker…"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140240,140240}…Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:24.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144077,144077}Maya… My Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:28.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148214,148214}I remember I was staring at her\Nlike this just a little over two years ago.
