Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166266,166266}A ticker for the play?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167567,167567}You can have it if you want it that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172072,172072}But only if you promise to do all the deliveries on New Year's Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180013,180013}You have to do them all by midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183483,183483}That means you have until all the ships\Nfinish sounding their horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194994,194994}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196196,196196}As I promised,\NI finished them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201067,201067}Give me the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203036,203036}F-Fine, if you want it that bad,\Nyou can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206706,206706}What is so important about this anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208808,208808}Here!\NGo get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216950,216950}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219352,219352}I can go!\NI can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221488,221488}I can go the play with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:43.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223490,223490}I had found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:45.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225492,225492}A girl of a thousand masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:47.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227527,227527}A girl who could play "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:50.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230397,230397}I took her to my new drama school, Tsukikage Theater…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:54.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234401,234401}…and determined how serious she was about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240874,240874}You can't be an actress as a hobby or for recreation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244244,244244}Can you dedicate your life to acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248581,248581}What are you going to do after you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250717,250717}I'll be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254320,254320}I want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260560,260560}Well said.\NThose are the words I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:26.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266766,266766}Maya joined my drama school, Tsukikage theater, and I gave her the role of Beth in "Little Women."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275842,275842}Emotions!\NEmotion will make the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279379,279379}Emotions…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284784,284784}No!\NThat's not Beth playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286619,286619}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:48.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288455,288455}I wanted to train her\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293393,293393}If you are here for the play rights for "The Crimson Goddess," you are wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:04:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298865,298865}I won't give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300400,300400}I will come back again and again\Ntill you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:03.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303370,303370}There were many who wanted\Nto get the play rights…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:06.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306406,306406}…for "The Crimson Goddess,"\Nwhich I received from Ozaki Ichiren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:09.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309809,309809}One of them was Hayami Masumi, the young president of Metropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:19.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319285,319285}Maya was struggling for her first role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326426,326426}Hey girl, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327994,327994}You'll catch a cold walking around\Nin the rain like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341307,341307}Wait for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343109,343109}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347881,347881}That's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351818,351818}Hey!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355722,355722}You… Uncle Laurence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:05:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359893,359893}Uncle Laurence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362095,362095}What are you talking about?\NIt's me, Hayami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365432,365432}Thank you for the music, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369502,369502}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374574,374574}Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377444,377444}Hey, are you okay?\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:21.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381881,381881}Uncle Laurence?\NMusic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:25.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385352,385352}"Little Women!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:31.72,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391725,391725}And the first day came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:34.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394027,394027}An actress, Himekawa Utako,\Nand her daughter, Himekawa Ayumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:37.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397230,397230}…along with Hayami Masumi from Metropolitan Entertainment and Director Onodera were all watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404204,404204}Teacher, Maya is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406272,406272}…has a fever of 40°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408441,408441}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410910,410910}There's no way she can be on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413546,413546}Teacher, I can play as a substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421755,421755}Maya, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424324,424324}I can do it.\NI can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426693,426693}What if you pass out on stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429229,429229}I'll get up.\NPlease let me play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433066,433066}I see. Go on.\NTry your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:20.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440473,440473}I am Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:24.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444978,444978}Maya continued on with a fever of 40°C.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:41.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461194,461194}A fever of 40°C and she grows\Neven more beautiful as the play goes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468468,468468}Beth, Beth, look at me.\NDon't die on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472639,472639}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475575,475575}Jill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478445,478445}Beth…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489956,489956}Beth is playing\Nthe piano in her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:22.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502202,502202}Maya's talent and passion\Nwere confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504938,504938}Great job, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508108,508108}Here's a gift from your fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510443,510443}It was left outside the backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512779,512779}"Please become\Na healthy Beth soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:36.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516149,516149}Purple roses were sent\Nby a secret admirer for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526026,526026}Madame, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.13,0:08:50.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530130,530130}At the time, I was devoted to how\NI would raise Maya as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537237,537237}She doesn't need letters from her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540273,540273}Here, let's burn the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542142,542142}Madame…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543610,543610}Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544778,544778}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545879,545879}What she needs now is separation from her past.\NNot to have anywhere to turn back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:10.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550917,550917}I severed all of Maya's ties to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556256,556256}A·me·n·bo·a·ka·i·sa·a·i·u·e·o.\NA·me…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564397,564397}Maya, your voice is the weakest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:27.90,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567901,567901}I trained Maya harder than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572205,572205}A·ga·i·sa…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574507,574507}Not good enough.\NMore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576009,576009}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:36.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576976,576976}Then my body was overcome\Nby a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:43.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583750,583750}Masumi's plan to acquire "The Crimson Goddess" was just starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:50.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590423,590423}I had to rely on Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:09:59.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599766,599766}Maya met my expectations very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:04.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604104,604104}As Midori in "Growing Up," she competed equally with the genius Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616483,616483}Goodbye, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:20.18,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620186,620186}In "Gena and the Five Blue Pots," she stood on stage by herself playing all 14 roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:47.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647047,647047}However, Tsukikage Theater was destroyed after all,\Nand all that was left…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:51.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651685,651685}…was an old church as a training hall and a few members, including Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656890,656890}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667400,667400}What is "The Crimson Goddess" really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669235,669235}I wonder if I can play\Nsuch a legendary role someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675975,675975}You can only play that role when you're able\Nto forget that you're a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681781,681781}There's no one that can play\N"The Crimson Goddess" now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685285,685285}Maya, you are far\Nfrom playing that role right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690090,690090}You must practice hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691925,691925}You need to be able to play\Nhundreds and thousands of roles to be able to play "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697564,697564}Teacher, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699165,699165}What type of person is the Crimson Goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701968,701968}The crimson Goddess is not a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705839,705839}She is… a plum tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712212,712212}A plum… tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716816,716816}Close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:03.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723690,723690}Encouraged by her passion for "The Crimson Goddess" and the purple roses…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:06.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726926,726926}…that were sent to her at every stage appearance, Maya sped along the actress' path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:10.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730230,730230}But the path of an actress\Nis still very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736002,736002}Heathcliff has done nothing wrong!\NNothing wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739205,739205}Get out of the way, Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746713,746713}But my body couldn't wait\Nfor Maya's development.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:31.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751785,751785}I couldn't die until I left "The Crimson Goddess" to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:36.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756322,756322}Maya, my Maya!
Comment: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:41.71,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:761718,761718}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:45.51,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:765515,765515}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:48.35,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:768351,768351}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768435,768435}Tōtō University Medical Center
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:50.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770070,770070}I started thinking about the next play\Nas soon as my condition got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:12:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776343,776343}Now, I'll announce the casting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779846,779846}I wonder what I will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782248,782248}I'm sure you'll play the main role.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786252,786252}Now, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786619,786619}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787787,787787}I will have you play a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790924,790924}A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792325,792325}Yes. A doll who just sits\Nin the middle of the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796563,796563}You won't have\Nany movements nor words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:18.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798365,798365}The challenge I gave her with this role was to empty her mind and to synchronize herself with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:29.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809676,809676}Deprived of movement, words,\Nany form of expression…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:34.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814414,814414}…Maya seemed to be successfully\Ncompleting the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:42.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822689,822689}The last day of\N"The Smile of Stone."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828361,828361}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835168,835168}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:56.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836936,836936}I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:02.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842809,842809}The mask is gone,\Nthe mask of a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848281,848281}What are you doing,\Ntaking your mask off on the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854120,854120}Because of your unprofessional behavior…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857023,857023}…this important last day of the play\Nwas almost jeopardized.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860460,860460}Teacher, Maya saw someone that seemed like her mother on the way to the theater today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866833,866833}It doesn't matter what it is, it still doesn't give you a reason to take your mask off on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871171,871171}Maya, you failed as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874507,874507}Failed…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876376,876376}You won't be in the next play.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878578,878578}You're on probation for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883516,883516}Probation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885318,885318}I knew I had to kill myself\Nbefore I went onto that stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.75,0:14:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889756,889756}You couldn't help it, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891558,891558}What we wear is a glass mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895795,895795}Glass mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897597,897597}Yes.\NA fragile glass mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900266,900266}That's why it's so easy to break it\Nand show the real face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:11.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911044,911044}Since her dream was so large,\Nshe was greatly disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:15.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915749,915749}I had to cast off her naivety.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927927,927927}Is this your shelter from the rain, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931064,931064}You… Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934801,934801}I can't let you go.\NYou are our important substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938838,938838}A substitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:46.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946680,946680}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:48.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948381,948381}Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:51.91,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951918,951918}The ad-lib that was exchanged between Kitajima Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:56.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956456,956456}…and Himekawa Ayumi was\Nsuch a surprising present to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967133,967133}I heard you declined\Nthe audition for Helen's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969469,969469}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970770,970770}You are afraid of Ayumi,\Nis that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972739,972739}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974174,974174}You got scared after being lead by Ayumi in "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979913,979913}Maya, you are hereby expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982649,982649}Expelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983983,983983}You knew you weren't allowed to get on stage, yet you took the role in "The Cherry Tree of Dream Festivals."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987921,987921}That's reason enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990256,990256}Expelled…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993126,993126}But, if you win the role of Helen,\Nthen I'll reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997630,997630}Helen's role?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999265,999265}If not, you can not only forget about practicing at my school, but "The Crimson Goddess" as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:47.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007240,1007240}Some cotton…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:51.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011978,1011978}…and some dressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:54.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014381,1014381}Helen's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:57.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017283,1017283}I'll live as Helen,\Nin the darkness and silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:01.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021221,1021221}Just as I planned, Maya practiced hard…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:05.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025692,1025692}…in a summer house provided by Mr. Purple Rose,\Ncausing scratches all over her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:10.33,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030330,1030330}Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:17.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037404,1037404}I already knew who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:21.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041941,1041941}But it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:24.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044644,1044644}If he could help Maya become an actress,\Nhe could have been the Devil himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:30.01,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050016,1050016}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:33.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053653,1053653}Oh, a rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:35.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055889,1055889}It's a rose.\NMr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:40.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060093,1060093}Finally!\NI finally get to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:43.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063863,1063863}The person who is\Nalways on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:47.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067067,1067067}Little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074107,1074107}What was that?\NHe just held me, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085752,1085752}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:07.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087921,1087921}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090357,1090357}We'll now start the audition\Nfor the role of Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095195,1095195}Here, we have\Nthe five candidates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:18.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098565,1098565}The audition finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:34.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114748,1114748}Maya. I knew she would meet my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127027,1127027}I hereby announce the decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131364,1131364}Helen Keller will be played by…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134200,1134200}…Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142409,1142409}And, also, by Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153386,1153386}We decided to double cast them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:17.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157157,1157157}Double cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:22.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162662,1162662}Maya won the role of Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:26.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166433,1166433}But if Ayumi's Helen was better…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:33.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173239,1173239}…then Ayumi would play\N"The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:39.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179045,1179045}I promised myself that only the best\Nwould play "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:47.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187320,1187320}What's wrong, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190056,1190056}I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:52.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192058,1192058}I'm afraid\Nto be compared with Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217450,1217450}Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228895,1228895}Wa… ter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.17,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240173,1240173}The battle was over…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:42.07,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242075,1242075}…and the overwhelming emotion by both actresses impressed me equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257957,1257957}Congratulations, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260827,1260827}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263296,1263296}But I still don't think\Nyou defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271738,1271738}Hello, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273206,1273206}Did you come to see your good student's award presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275508,1275508}A good student?\NYes, some future good students.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283149,1283149}Future good students?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300100,1300100}How are you, Miss Tsukikage?\NAny words of celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304571,1304571}Yes. Both Helens\Nhave some extraordinary talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308274,1308274}I must say they are suited to be candidates for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312979,1312979}Ms. Kitajima Maya, Ms. Himekawa Ayumi.\NPlease come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316649,1316649}Everyone, I would like to take advantage of this opportunity…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321054,1321054}…to introduce the two candidates for "The Crimson Goddess":\NKitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:14.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334668,1334668}From the stage to television.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:17.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337237,1337237}Maya has to step forward and take\Nnew challenges to grow as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:28.61,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348615,1348615}So does Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:31.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351751,1351751}The new battle for the two girls who aspire\Nto be "The Crimson Goddess" has just started.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:36.79,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356790,1356790}What's important is for you\Nto grow as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.19,0:22:43.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1363196,1363196}Go on, Maya!\NMy Maya!
Comment: 0,0:22:51.45,0:22:51.45,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1371453,1371453}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:23:01.25,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1375124,1381254}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
